 of stones, to set them, and in carving of timber, to work in all manner of workmanship.","year":-1491},{"id":"recXferXzOgCUKOU4","ref":"Exod.31.6","text":"And I, behold, I have given with him Aholiab, the son of Ahisamach, of the tribe of Dan: and in the hearts of all that are wise hearted I have put wisdom, that they may make all that I have commanded thee;","year":-1491},{"id":"recNQA9tJGF3EGSdg","ref":"Exod.31.7","text":"The tabernacle of the congregation, and the ark of the testimony, and the mercy seat that is thereupon, and all the furniture of the tabernacle,","year":-1491},{"id":"recfsZk3N1BbktgEe","ref":"Exod.31.8","text":"And the table and his furniture, and the pure candlestick with all his furniture, and the altar of incense,","year":-1491}]}
